lead_paragraph: Michael Young scored a season-high 26 points and No. 24 Pittsburgh held on after wasting a big lead for an 86-82 victory over Notre Dame on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Young Scores 25, No. 24 Pittsburgh Beats Notre Dame 86-82
